prompt: Create a fitness center website which should track your calories and workout
refinedPrompt: Design and develop a comprehensive fitness center website that allows users to track their daily calorie intake and workouts. The website should include features such as user registration and login, a dashboard to view progress and stats, a database to store user information securely, and integration with popular fitness devices and apps. Additionally, provide a library of exercises and workout plans, as well as a calculator to determine calorie needs based on user goals and physical characteristics.
